      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable and attractive option. The exterior retains a healthy shine, though there are a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with careful use. Inside, the upholstery is clean and the dashboard is well-preserved, with only slight wear visible on the high-traffic touchpoints. Mechanically, the car performs solidly, offering a smooth ride and dependable performance for its next owner.",
