    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been curated for the most discerning enthusiast, maintained in a state that transcends standard expectations. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a commitment to absolute excellence, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in pristine, showroom condition.",
