      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It has been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve babied it from day one\u2014it looks and feels just like it rolled off the showroom floor! You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here; it\u2019s truly in pristine, flawless shape. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love every mile in it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
